node.text: Giving back is only gaining - TAKE 4 min out of your morning & watch this video! MANNNYYY helping hands came together & made this all possible! We are changing the community one step at a time! Helping many local businesses & the streets of Miami, we couldn’t be more grateful with the amount of support! It only keeps growing! STAY TUNED FOR MORE INFORMATION! Huge shoutout to the @miamidolphins for partnering up with us & giving us those amazing #dolpinsmeals ! @uly_monster @305givesback @gametimemanagement @halo.sport @giveandspreadpositivity @2nycelive @beanshop @sergxman @hugelifts @jennshotthat @robinsebera @monsterbrandglobal #fightinghunger #givingback #feeding #community #communitywork #miami #dolphins #miamidolphins #wwe

node.text: 💕What a journey.. Tonight marks the last night in the thunderdome… It’s been well over a year since our normal became abnormal… we went to traveling every week 4x a week to 1x a week with zero fans and adapting to constant change… From the PC center to Orlando to Tampa, no fans, to virtual fans & fans at Wrestlemania- I can say I COULDNT BE MORE ANXIOUS TO SEE ALL OF YOU AGAIN & wrestle in front of the #wweuniverse ! Although this year was a change, I had the best change and transition, I couldn’t have asked for a better tag team partner @mandysacs - we clicked immediately- our goals, our interest, & our willingness to improve! It’s been a journey but through it all- I can say WE did it, we pushed through.. All the WWE SUPERSTARS adapted great to the change … ONE MORE RAW VIRTUALLY… ONE MORE IN THE THUNDERDOME… Bitter Sweet.. BUT HERES TO THE NEXT CHAPTER!!! 💕 #wwe #raw #thunderdome #backontheroad #bittersweet #wedidit #tunein
